      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67a2e86225596.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688752947d81f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b559462331a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6deec146d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6e0f18c89.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/679875c026681.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f32e4fb0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f35b8eb9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f3f2c9de.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/679875c0e297a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f3b60be3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/689af7d666ee6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6e403379b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67b65b6dde32e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b01f5f5288c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f209fefd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0b75b468c2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67bf52a321a2d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ac721d1c753.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/689afa8a3b7d7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0f99950501.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0b59272679.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0b5a41d9c8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0b5b21a9a3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0f8bd8d9f3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b559e5993a4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0f92d31f28.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b6a076ddc25.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0f9cfa12df.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0b5801e78b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0fa2b475cc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b762e7eba11.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68af6f2e044dd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d429e1cea4d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b7632141d33.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b93006b26d3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b93088dcb29.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b9300e75721.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688753a8bc19c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0fa7ec61b7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b19107aa20f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Can't stop. Won't Stop.&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since my last posting, titled "Mission Complete", I never actually stopped working on the mod. lol&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;In anticipation of Metroid Prime 4, I added a color option for the power armor that resembles the armor seen in the Metroid Prime 4 teaser trailer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Changed the lights on the power armor to match the lights from the visor. Now instead of blue, the lights will be based on lore accuracy or past appearances.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added install options to change between Super Jump, Infinite Sprinting, Super Jump + Infinite Sprinting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;fixed more icons for menus and inventory.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Changed most places that say "Link" to now say "Samus", along with other dialogue and text fixes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Changed more text and logos that say "Legend of Zelda" to instead say "Legend of Samus".&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added a file to the downloads called "Logo &amp;amp; Icons" that changes the CEMU icons and a few other things. Unzip it and follow the README instructions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added an option to choose whether you want to use the Ridley armor mod or Torizo (Chozo) Armor mod. Icons included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;All armors that didn't have special effects now have Attack Up as the effect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Armor effects are now upgradeable! When you upgrade at a fairy fountain, your armor effects will upgrade too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3xtbZJItcKM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;*The video above does not show the latest updates, like icons, descriptions, or armor mixing, but still showcases the main features.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Hello Metroid fans :)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;Ever wanted to explore the world of Hyrule as Samus Aran? Now you can!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;INCLUDES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;All Armors are made to look like different Suits from the series.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Armor colors are designed to be lore accurate, but also allow for mixing and matching.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;All armors now have bonuses that will upgrade with the armors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All bows &amp;amp; arrows are made to look and act like Armguns &amp;amp; beams with sounds and effects.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 Beam types and Missiles instead of arrows. Optional arrow crafting and bundle multipliers.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Power Bombs, Scan Visor, Grapple Beam, Samus' Gunship, and even a Metroid paraglider.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;New hand-made icons and descriptions for everything listed above and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Beautiful main menu artwork hand-made to look like Samus in the style of BOTW art.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sound effects and music from the Metroid series.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Many more little details.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;*No AI was involved in this entire project. All icons and artwork are hand made with GIMP.&amp;nbsp; Just to give you an idea, there are over 3000 edited files in this modpack. Check out my &lt;a href="//patreon.com/TheOnlyQuarry"&gt;Patreon&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for more of my content.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;INSTALLATION&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on the yellow links below to start your downloads.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag all your downloaded zip/bnp files into UKMM (do not unzip files).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reorder your mods to match the order you see below.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Activate UKMM in your graphics packs in CEMU.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Play game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;*BCML is outdated and will not load zip files. UKMM fixes a lot of bugs and these mods will work much better with it.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;*To install the Logo &amp;amp; Icons zip, just unzip and follow the README instructions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;RECCOMMENDED MODS AND LOAD ORDER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Other people's mods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/552265"&gt;Arrow Bundle Multiplier&lt;/a&gt; (Optional)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/957663"&gt;Improved Invisible Sheikah Slate&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/958211"&gt;Invisible Sheathed Weapons&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/484227"&gt;Early Master Cycle Zero&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/466677"&gt;Samus Mod&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(REQUIRED)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/493411"&gt;Fusion Suit&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(REQUIRED)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/496551"&gt;Torizo Set&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(REQUIRED)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/436412"&gt;Ridley Armor&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(REQUIRED)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/476498"&gt;Wild Running&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(REQUIRED)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/666973"&gt;Summerset Voicepack&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;My Mod fixes&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/1387716"&gt;Crafting Project REpack&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;My Mods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/1512596"&gt;The Legend of Samus Breath of the Wild&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Bonus!&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/1510852"&gt;Logo &amp;amp; Icons&lt;/a&gt; for Cemu and Desktop. Unzip and read README for install instructions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Other Optional Mods (Causes conflicts. Not fully tested)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.patreon.com/sockpoppet" target="_blank"&gt;Varia Suit&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Optional. May not actually work with this mod anymore. Also costs $.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/dl/964367"&gt;Remove Pouch and Belt&lt;/a&gt; (Optional. Conflicts with player model, but looks great when armored.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;DETAILS OF FEATURES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Logo &lt;/span&gt;- Changes the title screen to show Samus instead. I used original game art and ran them through filters in GIMP to make them blend with the BOTW art style.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Armgun &lt;/span&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Replaces every bow model in the game with Samus' Armgun and makes them shoot in a straight line. Affects enemy bows and Includes icons and descriptions too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Beams &lt;/span&gt;- Changes the arrows to have cool new effects and descriptions.&amp;nbsp;Includes 5 different beam types and Hyper Missiles! Affects enemy arrows too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Power Bomb&lt;/span&gt;- Replaces both bombs to look like the Power Bomb in the classic series.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Scan Visor&lt;/span&gt; - Changes the Camera to instead look like the Scan Visor. (Now in High resolution!)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Grapple Beam&lt;/span&gt; - Changes the Magnesis name and icon to the Grapple Beam.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Upgrades&lt;/span&gt; - Changes Heart and Stamina tanks into Energy Tanks and Missile Expansions. The health bar (heart shape) has been replaced with square energy bars.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mobility&lt;/span&gt; - Increases jump height by about 3 times and removes stamina consumption from sprinting. All other stamina related actions remain the same. Place after Wild Running in your load order.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Armor &lt;/span&gt;- All armors have been replaced with various outfits from the metroid series. The best part is that every armor set can be upgraded and recolored, even the ones that normally aren't. Colors have also been designed to allow for mixing and matching. Lastly, all inventory icons and descriptions have been updated for each armor/color/upgrade. Original armor models are from Samus Mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Gunship &lt;/span&gt;- Master Cycle Zero has been replaced with Samus' Gunship. Download the optional Early Master Cycle Zero mod to play around with the gunship instead of having to ride a horse everywhere.&amp;nbsp;This is part of the Samus mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Metroid &lt;/span&gt;- The paraglider has been replaced with a baby metroid. This is part of the Samus mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Icons and Descriptions&lt;/span&gt; - All icons and descriptions have been edited for every armor/color/upgrade, every armgun, most sheikah tools, the paraglider, and some menu icons. All made with GIMP. No AI.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Save File&lt;/span&gt; -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;I added a save file to the downloads for anyone that wants to start their game with the armors and armgun for either cosplay or testing purposes. This save file is optional and there's nothing stopping you from enjoying the game like normal. The file can be edited easily with an &lt;a href="https://www.marcrobledo.com/savegame-editors/zelda-botw/" target="_blank"&gt;Online Save Editor&lt;/a&gt;. (This is an old idea and the game has since been tailored for a full normal playthrough. If you're worried about a lack of arrows, just download all the optional mods that add more arrows or allow for crafting arrows.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Included in the Save File:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;999 Normal/Fire/Ice/Electric Arrows&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;10 Bomb Arrows&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 Ancient Arrows&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ancient/Wild/Rubber/Phantom Armor Sets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Samus' Armgun&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Motorcycle Unlocked&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Clarification about the mods on my page:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;I am not providing a copy of Samus mod or any content from the mods listed in the section "Other people's mods". The links on my page directly download from the pages of the respective mod authors. The author list can be found in the credits section at the top of the page. I did this to avoid having to open up 20 tabs just to download this modpack and the downloads don't count towards my page, but instead go towards their respective owners. To reiterate: I AM NOT PROVIDING CONTENT OR MODS THAT ARE NOT MADE BY ME. That would be plagiarism. However, mods listed under "My mods", are in fact, made by me and can also be found in the normal download section Just click through the "recommended" list with the yellow links. Furthermore, The majority of the Metroid related content is actually part of the Samus Mod. My mods just build off of that mod by changing colors, mechanics or file paths, but do not provide any models or music from the Metroid franchise.&lt;/em&gt;</description>
