      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688b24470c9ea.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688b09e3a6bcc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d45494dc4c7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688b24a507dc6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/645609b4179b7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/645609b2eb102.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/645609b418224.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/645609b40e57c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/645609b3d88c6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163032191be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63de758f94974.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63de755467e99.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6379ee491ce6d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6379ee4ad3d18.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6379ee48caf78.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6379ee4a32fc8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/633d48ac3cc5b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/633d48ac475fd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/630f17213edd5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee686bcad.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee68adfe1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee69775e8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee686423c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee6871fd6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6311ee6583948.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d45485350ee.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630e2521f4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630e2283d1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630dde175d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163239e6d95.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630d0b083f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416323ccb669.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163232d0e34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416322007081.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416324202fd7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641632455d60d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; DAR 3.5&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Brand New Soulslike Skills System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Read the wiki for details: &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://dark-army-resurrection.fandom.com/wiki/Skills_Systems"&gt;https://dark-army-resurrection.fandom.com/wiki/Skills_Systems&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added New Enemy Ancient Lynels&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;They will randomly spawn in some areas after you reach Calamity Level 2, you can also find one in the Zora Mountain, they will be equipped with ancient weapons and a unique ancient bow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Special Thanks to BANAN039 for the Ancient Lynel Model.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Ancient Bombs Bow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Bow is equipped by Ancient Lynels and after you get one, there is a chance to find it inside chests as well. This bow can throw 3 Ancient Bombs and it can be used 25 times before it breaks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Champion Ancient Bombs Bow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you have an Ancient Bomb Bow in your equipment, when you activate Sheikah Spirit, you will find the Champion Ancient Bombs Bow, this bow can shoot 5 Ancient Bombs Arrows and like all others Spirits Weapons, it's unbreakable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ New Illusory Blight Fight Challenges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Illusory Blights Fights has been reworked in order to offer you a brand new challenge, basically you gonna face Illusory Blights using Ancient Spirit form and Weapons but you need to defeat Illusory Blights without getting hit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added new module 'CUSTOM PLAYER STATS' (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With this module you can deeply customize your player Stats and Stamina, so if you find this mod too hard or too easy, you can refine Link stats to balance your gameplay experience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Module needs to have higher priority in BCML.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Module is available only in DELUXE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Elemental Enemies Explosions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elemental enemies will explode after they die so pay extra attention on them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Chests Prohibition message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added 'Hard Monk Boss' option (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The last fight against the Priest Boss is gonna be harder.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This option is gonna be active in FREE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added 'DAR custom stats with Original Stamina' option (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This option is gonna be available only in DELUXE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Random Spawning Chests, Iron and Wooden Boxes all over Hyrule&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added 'No drop animation on Terminals' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This will remove the annoing drop animation when using some terminals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Special Thanks to NEBROC which is the creator of this option.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Changed Double Lynel Axe with Lynel Reaper&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Special Thanks to SOCKPOPPET for the Lynel Reaper Model.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Improved Shrine of Resurrection Chests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the first chest you gonna find one upper and one lower armor, in the second chest a random head gear plus 2 random items.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Improveed Punitive Death and Punitive Blood Moon messages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed Trials of the Sword&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now it works also when the option 'Harder Enemies' is enabled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed all Divine Beasts Challenges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed Lynel Dash attacks not hitting Link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Increased Souls and Red Stars drops&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Start New Game during Night&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you start a new game, it will be during night time and it's gonna be a blood moon night (the first Blood Moon won't hurt you in case you are using Punitive Blood Moon)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Kilton's Shops are unlocked from the begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can buy Souls and Red Stars in exchange of Monster Parts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;- Red Stars have been removed from Beedle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed a bug where Spiritual Weapons could be use by Regular Link.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Ancient Spirit Timer will now upgrade when gettin new Ancients Spirits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed Enemies Scaling Levels&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Limits for Lynel's Reaper and Whip Sword&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now you can carry just one lynel's reape and max 3 whip swords&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Red Stars will now fall from the sky&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added auto upgrade options for Wallets, Quivers and Red Stars Limit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since looking for Korok Seeds is really boring, I've added an Auto Upgrade System for Wallets, Quivers and Red Stars Limit, you can change this option throgh Campfire Menu&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Ancient Spirit Timer will be set to 30 seconds inside Divine Beasts during Bosses fights&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ You need to kill the Ancient Lynel on top of Zora mountain before starting Sidon fight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;* Fixed Dragons not spawning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Completing Ballad of Heroes quest will unlock Light Spirit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Light Spirit is gonna be the strongest Ancient Spirit but will consume double of the Ancient Spirit Timer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added options to disable Link's Pouch, Belts and Chest Belt models&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Bokoblin Slayer Armor compatibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bokoblin Slayer Armor is now fully integrated in Random Chests System, you can also choose to start a new game with Bokoblin Slayer Set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Disable Cooking option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Disable Wood Bundle option so you can only save at Campfires Stables and Beds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Sheikah Batteries Limits has been enanced to 10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Updated Second Wind patch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now DAR it's compatible with Second Wind version v1.9.14-alpha-6.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When playing with SW, there is an option in the patch where you can choose to have Lynels drops Lynel Grudges after they die.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Fixed HardCore Chests (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This option is available only in DELUXE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Improved Random Chests Rupees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Enhanced Hixox health&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added 'Less Sunny Weather' option (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This option is gonna be active in FREE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added 'Harder Hyrule Castle' option (DELUXE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hyrule Castle Area is gonna be bigger and inside this Area the weather is always gonna be Thunderstorm and the sky is gonna be like the one of the Blood Moon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This option is gonna be active in FREE version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;+ Added Elemental Malice Lizalfos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elemental Malice Lizalfos will randomly Spawn inside Hyrule Castle and in Harder Divine Beasts, they gonna be equipped with spiritual weapons.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.patreon.com/posts/dark-army-3-5-135366895"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download Dark Army Resurrection Deluxe 3.5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thank you all for your support!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Happy Summer to everyone!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ENJOY!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you like this mod please consider making a &lt;a href="https://paypal.me/miirkuz" target="_blank"&gt;DONATION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&#13;
&lt;b&gt;Concept&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;br&gt;Something went wrong with the ritual that awakened Link, maybe Zelda &#13;
said the wrong words, who knows, the fact is that the Dark Army has been&#13;
 awakened.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
I'm Miirkuz, a mod creator for Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild with 3 years experience and &lt;strong&gt;Dark Army Resurrection&lt;/strong&gt; is my main project.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
With &lt;strong&gt;more than 2 years&lt;/strong&gt; of developing and &lt;strong&gt;more than 40.000 downloads&lt;/strong&gt;, DAR has become pretty popular even because some of the most important streamers have been playing with DAR for months.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
This mod add tons of unique features to the original game like a &lt;strong&gt;Skill System&lt;/strong&gt; based on collecting &lt;strong&gt;Souls&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Locked Chests System&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Spawning Enemies&lt;/strong&gt;, lots of &lt;strong&gt;Unique Weapons&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Death&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Blood Moon&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Replayable Divine Beasts&lt;/strong&gt; and many many more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
The thing that makes this mod unique is the fact that you can &lt;strong&gt;customize&lt;/strong&gt; it using &lt;strong&gt;more than 100 options&lt;/strong&gt; and some of them are selectable in game through a &lt;strong&gt;Campfire Menu&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
Join &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/Xcrf7cSwP9" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Dark Army Resurrection Discord Server&lt;/a&gt; to get full support, updates, beta versions, troubleshooting and more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
This mod require a specific procedure to be installed correctly, so make sure to check &lt;a href="https://dark-army-resurrection.fandom.com/wiki/Dark_Army_Resurrection_Wiki"&gt;DAR Official Wiki &lt;/a&gt;for full details.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Versions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Starting from version 3.0 the release method is gonna be different, there are gonna be 2 different versions.&#13;
I've decided to setup a Patreon Page for DAR.&#13;
On the &lt;a href="https://www.patreon.com/DarkArmyResurrection" target="_blank"&gt;Patreon Page&lt;/a&gt; you'll find the &lt;b&gt;DELUXE &lt;/b&gt;version. You'll find all subscription details on the Patreon Page.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I'll keep providing a &lt;b&gt;FREE &lt;/b&gt;version on Gamebanana but it's gonna be a Single Module built with my Preset Options, you gonna have very limited install options and in game options will be disabled.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Suggested Mods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;To improve the Dark Atmosphere of this mod I suggest to try&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/426534"&gt; DAR Enemies Recolor&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/428063"&gt;DAR Official Reshade&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Discord Server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;br&gt;Join &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/Xcrf7cSwP9" target="_blank"&gt;Dark Army Resurrection Discord Server&lt;/a&gt; to get full support, updates, beta versions, troubleshoting and more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&#13;
&lt;b&gt;Special&#13;
Thanks&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
